               <p>(<hi rend="italic">The</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">considered that the two witnesses for the Defence had grossly perjured themselves; upon which they were committed to prison until the close of the Session, when they were discharged</hi>).</p>
